{"tid":870585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共軍新技能 手牽手進地雷區用腳掃雷","createTime":"2018-10-21T08:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T11:32:18.000Z","uid":72009,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ded28f072b757ce98c40183f5ee471160f9e78","tid":870585,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181021/1451506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181021%2F1451506&d=BqY1nZ9xAMQx3w6LkQeDmAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=e3adab2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181021%2F1451506&h=aa6dcfde\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181021/1451506</a><br />\n<br />\n中國央視網10月18日，分享士兵手牽手進地雷區驗收掃雷成果的影片，宣稱是「大無畏的革命精神」，讓中國網友吐槽「這價值觀有毛病」、「這不叫勇氣自信，叫草菅人命」、「領導不把士兵當人」。<br />\n<br />\n據《自由亞洲電台》報導，從央視網的影片可看到，解放軍們手牽手唱著歌，走入中越邊境的地雷區，官方也宣，解放軍們無謂生死、在用腳查探有否殘餘地雷，現在沒有哪個國家的軍隊，有如此的勇氣和自信。<br />\n觀察人士傅先生指出，這舉動反映軍隊並沒有把士兵的生命當作一回事，「就是想通過這種（行動），來煽動一個所謂的愛國情結，就跟那個抗洪搶險士兵上去肉搏是一個理。完全沒有理性、沒有邏輯。」<br />\n影片曝光後，中國網友也紛紛留言「這是在拿年輕的生命開玩笑吧」、「叫隻豬上去跑不就好了」、「拿生並當兒戲」、「人多也不能這樣操作」、「我們繳了稅，買台排雷車好嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181021/640_3a26dd4b67899f3aa6c6c3ec811826c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181021%2F640_3a26dd4b67899f3aa6c6c3ec811826c6.jpg&h=7f2a7863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181021/640_fe8b787099f026b7c53feb3d80e2c64c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181021%2F640_fe8b787099f026b7c53feb3d80e2c64c.jpg&h=b616b757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b42e13177ee505f575e23d7466100d0a419a91f","tid":870585,"uid"